Package io.github.ai4ci

Annotation Type Data

public @interface Data
Central annotation for configuring Immutables value types with consistent styling and Jackson serialization support across the codebase.

This annotation and its nested styles provide standardized configurations for Immutables-generated value types, ensuring consistency in:

  • Accessor method naming patterns
  • Builder initialization patterns
  • Jackson serialization/deserialization behavior
  • Hash code, equals, and toString implementations
  • Pluralization handling for collection properties

Usage Examples

 @Data.Style
 public interface Person {
     String getName();
     int getAge();
 }

Each nested annotation provides specialized styling for different use cases while maintaining overall consistency across the codebase.
